OL,3,CHidden camera discovered in government
OL,4,Coffices
OL,6,FA hidden camera has been found in a
OL,7,Fceiling panel in a government building.
OL,9,FThe electronic device was found in a
OL,10,FWestminster complex where the Home
OL,11,FOffice; Ministry of Housing,
OL,12,FCommunities and Local Government
OL,13,F(MHCLG) and the Department for
OL,14,FEnvironment, Food and Rural Affairs
OL,15,F(DEFRA) are based.
OL,17,FThe camera was discovered within the
OL,18,Fpast two months and the security
OL,19,Fservices have been informed.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
