OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1781002969
OL,3,CHidden camera discovered in government
OL,4,Coffices
OL,6,FIt is understood to have been found in
OL,7,Fa communal area of the shared building
OL,8,Frather than around ministerial offices.
OL,10,FThe complex, located near the Houses
OL,11,Fof Parliament, is the base for the
OL,12,FHome Office, responsible for policing
OL,13,Fand national security and MHCLG, which
OL,14,Ftook decisions relating to the
OL,15,Fplanning permission for the
OL,16,Fcontroversial new Chinese embassy in
OL,17,FLondon.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
